Package: fieldwalkr
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Sampling and Survey Simulation Tools
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-02-21
Authors@R: person("Joe", "Roe", email = "jwg983@hum.ku.dk",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: fieldwalkr is a simulation framework for spatial surveys 
    (fieldwalking in archaeologists' jargon), intended to be useful for
    exploring, designing, and evaluation sampling strategies.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.2)
License: CC0
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
  spatstat (>= 1.43),
  akima
